LogChipper.NET v1.0.0 by ewall, November 2012
(c)2012 Eric W. Wallace / MaineHealth

Description:
  Tails a log file and sends all writes to a remote syslog daemon.

Usage:
  Runs as a Windows service, which is configured during the setup (included).

Requires:
  .NET Framework 3.5

Version History:
  1.0.0 - initial release
  
TODO/Wishlist:
